---
title: Let's Imagine Behaviors
updated: 2015-11-02 20:06
---

As I've been led to understand, describing behaviors is better than trying to program actions into as many various critters as we expect to populate this world with. There is a decent [Tuts roundup](http://gamedevelopment.tutsplus.com/series/understanding-steering-behaviors--gamedev-12732) of these sorts of things, so we'll plan for some of our plants first.

### Plant Behaviors
